      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A call has been issued for a public\nmeeting to be held in the offices of\nthe chamber of commerce at 10 a. m.\nWednesday to perfect the formation\nOf branch of the National Irrigation\nassociation. George H. Maxwell,\nchairman of the National association\nand the Spokane delegates to the re-\nGently held Transmississippi Com\nmercia1 congress at Seattle. will be\npresent to address the meeting.\n\n\nSome time on Wednesday the\nGreat Northern special immigration\ntrain will be in the city from the\nSound. Levi g. Monroe is arrang-\ning to have the local real estate deal\ners meet the immigration officials."
    }
